 n sign reads "Beware of the Wumpus!"\nThere are tunnels to rooms 2\, 6\, a
 nd 10.\nYou hear a faint clicking noise. (There are spiders in room 6)\n(M
 )ove or (S)hoot?\nM\nWhich room?\n5\nDimwit! You can't get to there from h
 ere.\nThere are tunnels to rooms 2\, 6\, and 10.\n(M)ove or (S)hoot?\nM\nW
 hich room?\n2\n\nYou are in room 2.\nYou have 3 arrows left.\nThere is a b
 lack pool of water in the corner.\nThere are tunnels to rooms 1\, 3\, and 
 7.\nYou smell a dank odor. (There is a pit in room 3)\nYou smell some nast
 y Wumpus! (The wumpus is in room 7)\n(M)ove or (S)hoot?\nS\nWhich room?\n3
